    "description": "We've deconstructed a classic BLT and turned it into a delicious warm salad. You'll serve up crispy bacon shards with roasted potatoes, avocado, lettuce, shallot rings and juicy cherry tomatoes, all drizzled with a zippy mustard mayo dressing. Yum!",
