    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Drizzle them with<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 10 min</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper, then chop in half widthways</p><p>Shred the bottom half of the<strong> lettuce</strong> finely</p><p>Separate the <strong>remaining lettuce leaves</strong>, keeping them whole</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and roughly chop</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>After an initial 10 min, add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to the tray with the <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 20-25 min or until the potatoes are cooked through and the bacon is crisp</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>mayo </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> water</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>avocado</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>roasted potatoes</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>mustard dressing </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-bacon-lettuce-tomato-and-avocado-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>crispy bacon</strong> into rough pieces</p><p>Serve the <strong>crispy bacon pieces</strong> over the <strong>dressed salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>mustard dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
